---
---
<section class="hero glass-panel">
    <p class="eyebrow">Full Stack Software Engineer </br> .NET • Java • Angular • Azure • AWS</p>
    <h1>Building scalable solutions and real-world systems.</h1>
    <p class="bio">
        Full Stack Software Engineer focused on building reliable applications, 
        scalable backend systems, improving engineering workflows, and delivering reliable solutions across complex environments.
    </p>
    <div class="btns">
        <a href="/#projects" class="btn-primary">View projects</a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn-secondary">More about me</a>
    </div>

    <div class="glow-orb"></div>
</section>

<style>
    .hero {
        position: relative;
        padding: 64px 40px;
        margin: 40px 0;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-align: center;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .eyebrow {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent-main);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        z-index: 1;
    }
    h1 {
        font-size: 42px;
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        z-index: 1;
    }
    .bio {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 550px;
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        z-index: 1;
    }
    .btns {
        display: flex;
        gap: 16px;
        z-index: 1;
    }
    .btn-primary {
        background: var(--accent-main);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 12px 28px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 14px var(--accent-glow);
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
        background: var(--accent-secondary);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-secondary {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        color: var(--text-primary);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-glass);
        padding: 12px 28px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-color: var(--accent-main);
    }
    
    .glow-orb {
        position: absolute;
        top: -50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 300px;
        height: 300px;
        background: var(--accent-glow);
        filter: blur(80px);
        border-radius: 50%;
        z-index: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .btns {
            display: block;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
    }
</style>
